Vulois got a shocked look an his face after Afterburner's 
transmission. Child had come into the tunnel? ALONE?!? He immediatly 
turned to Windrazor.

"Stay by the machine and see if there's a message from Battera. I'm 
going to find Child!"

Vulois ran out of the entrance and back into the darkness.

"Child! Where are you Child?"
